10:13 Kuko yavuze ati “Narabikoze ubwanjye mbikoresheje imbaraga z'ukuboko kwanjye n'ubwenge bwanjye, kuko ndi umunyabwenge. Nakuyeho ingabano z'amahanga, nanyaze ubutunzi bwabo, nagize ubutwari, nimikūra abari bicaye ku ntebe z'ubwami.
