10:18 Kandi azamaraho ubwiza bw'ishyamba rye, n'ubw'imirima ye yera cyane, azamaraho n'ubugingo n'umubiri, hazabaho ubwihebe nk'uko bimera iyo ūtwara ibendera yiheba.
